<p>本人主要参考<a href='https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ac411B7Li/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click&amp;vd_source=1dbfcdd3bc12c44e3250e5e230a45acf'>超详细！个人博客搭建教程，低成本，零代码，手把手，WordPress<em>哔哩哔哩</em>bilibili</a></p>
<h3 id="scMtM">1.购买服务器</h3>
<p><font style="color:rgb(24, 25, 28);"></font></p>
<blockquote><p><font style="color:rgb(24, 25, 28);">首先登陆 WordPress官网  <a href='https://cn.wordpress.org/' target='_blank' class='url'>https://cn.wordpress.org/</a></font></p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730468757484-8239969e-a2ce-4973-92e4-645ddde95d8d.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>下载完成后进入<font style="color:rgb(24, 25, 28);">彩虹云主机官网：<a href='https://www.cccyun.net/' target='_blank' class='url'>https://www.cccyun.net/</a></font></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730468872313-5724c2d2-4c69-490e-b216-1e0571e8f4ca.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>这里推荐购买香港高速主机</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730468969197-36c5222e-bb5a-4775-88ee-c7d421b42519.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>进入控制面板，并将下载的文件放入wwwroot</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730469051187-eee71681-6800-4545-b907-710bafd4dac6.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>这里文件解压没有密码（直接处理即可）</p>
<h3 id="RWzxH">2.购买域名</h3>
<blockquote><p>这里本人使用的是百度云</p>
</blockquote>
<p>首先进入百度云官网，进入域名服务</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730534414039-c7053707-5f39-46b9-818c-ac708047be15.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>购买好域名后，进入控制台。（需要系统实名认证，可能要等待一些时间）</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730534566076-bcece279-df8a-48d4-8b6f-00dff1608e05.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730540450507-cb80652b-7fc7-4e05-a2b7-6ca327522882.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>进入域名管理并解析到之前注册的香港主机。（这里注意：主机记录直接填写www，然后记录类型选择CNAME记录）</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730534688696-a5c6f1ef-452a-45e7-8621-f5c196b1cbcc.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>绑定成功后可以到控制面板中查询（如上图所示）</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="ljAvI">3.将域名和主机绑定</h3>
<blockquote><p>之后只需要将购买的主机中添加域名</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730535065485-9d211c78-3b9a-45ac-9ddc-19ba977137bc.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>在浏览器中搜索你所注册的域名（<a href='http://www.xenonpeach.top' target='_blank' class='url'>www.xenonpeach.top</a>)出现该页面即证明之前步骤成功</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730540624752-0adb028b-c060-44ec-8806-f6fe0d759a4e.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>点击“现在就开始&quot;后进入以下页面，回到彩虹云主机（找到已开通产品）</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730540944159-401fef12-6993-46e4-9d98-c97ba8db8945.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>将以上信息复制粘贴值如下的数据库链接中</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730540814726-0fe5161f-1bff-4b73-b3da-421db649ce85.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>回到百度云，进入控制页面后将购买的域名信息复制粘贴，并填写网站管理者信息（尤其要记住用户名和密码，因为此后操作需要进入）</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730535332960-ba625c48-7dfe-4e33-b2b0-76cf1cba3ce1.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 id="h5vBV">成果</h2>
<blockquote><p>最后点击创建即可</p>
</blockquote>
<p>最开始进入网站时是如下图所示（是Wordpress的初始模式）</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730541192400-d39c837b-eb7d-4709-b86c-efc739f7ee7f.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>可以进行编辑（如删除初始模式，选择自定义）</p>
<p>本人在这里只是简单的更换了一下主题</p>
<p>然后还可以在这里发布文章，进行评论</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730541446991-3d2b612f-cee4-48a6-8b88-13b5137ea1db.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
<p>可以通过浏览器进行搜索<a href='http://www.xenonpeach.top' target='_blank' class='url'>www.xenonpeach.top</a></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/49936975/1730536097400-512e4552-41af-4190-85a4-a969f9a6cb8e.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
